    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBAPR/status/2033627361154064874",
      "reply_text": "Interesting mix of vets and young talent. Shai's breakout season is worth a look.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:34:08.598795+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/do5ei/status/2033640022658678805",
      "reply_text": "Impressive resume. How do you think the 12x VCC wins will translate to the NAC?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:34:46.637566+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/PaulGarciaNBA/status/2033637357434421255",
      "reply_text": "Big blow for LA",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:35:29.000913+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LineupsWinning/status/2033638277308420558",
      "reply_text": "Makes sense with that injury list. He's been getting more minutes",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:36:01.261502+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TheCollinDunks/status/2033635714232160363",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, his athleticism is wasted when he's not on the court",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:36:33.066688+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/WireHoops/status/2033634781938729057",
      "reply_text": "Not sure about Irving on the Magic. They need a true center, not a guard.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:37:14.486449+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LAClippersFilm/status/2033634482969063512",
      "reply_text": "That's a tough one for LAC. Hip fractures can take time to heal.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:37:59.308794+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BrettSiegelNBA/status/2033627672685768938",
      "reply_text": "Booker's case is strong, but Kawhi's playoff resume still stands out",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:38:44.768032+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BySamGordon/status/2033599345262506352",
      "reply_text": "Missing Green's presence will be felt. Warriors' bench needs to step up.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:39:34.894054+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/celtics/status/2033641979524120853",
      "reply_text": "Still gets the blood pumping",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:49:39.052788+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Hero_OfThe_Day/status/2033641081787515330",
      "reply_text": "Not sure why Luka's getting snubbed. He's been playing out of his mind all season",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:50:21.968509+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/SleeperHeat/status/2033635453409083642",
      "reply_text": "Congrats to Bam, well-deserved. He's been playing strong defense all season.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:51:00.294371+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/ClutchPoints/status/2033609501182423221",
      "reply_text": "Fair take. Embiid's dominance is undeniable.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:51:39.809902+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/SleeperTWolves/status/2033632942736461947",
      "reply_text": "Those records don't tell the whole story. Home and away splits matter.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T20:52:16.293566+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TheTruth8240/status/2033636715919999162",
      "reply_text": "That's a harsh take but fair. Finals are a different beast.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T21:02:10.841968+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBACobwebs/status/2033646771352600618",
      "reply_text": "44 points from Jalen Rose in double OT? That's clutch.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T21:02:43.845303+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/OutlierDotBet/status/2033646693951115618",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, he's been cooking. Love the volume",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T21:03:25.351041+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/krishcoughran/status/2033625106438869133",
      "reply_text": "That's a clear distinction. Load management is a luxury few teams have.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T21:04:03.748202+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LandofNix/status/2033635967874306315",
      "reply_text": "That's just the rumor mill. We need actual news.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T21:04:46.573249+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBA__Courtside/status/2033640255669088394",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, point guard is a grind. Most rookies don't get that kind of responsibility.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-16T21:16:27.102736+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/SNYKPodHarlem/status/2033640903915491718",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, playing undrafted guys over picks is a questionable strategy. You gotta think about the future.",
